\pard\keepn\sb360\sa120\b\fs32 9. Export Formats\b0\fs24\par
\pard\li360\sb30\sa30\bullet  \b GeoJSON\b0  \u8212? Probability contour polygons for GIS tools (QGIS, Mapbox, ArcGIS)\par
\bullet  \b CZML\b0  \u8212? Cesium globe time-dynamic visualization format\par
\bullet  \b Binary\b0  \u8212? Unity binary format for fast runtime data loading\par
\bullet  \b CSV\b0  \u8212? Full grid data (index, x, y, z, probability) for external analysis\par
\pard\keepn\sb360\sa120\b\fs32 10. Physics Model\b0\fs24\par
\pard\sb60\sa60 The CSharpNumerics PlumeSimulator implements the Gaussian Plume/Puff atmospheric dispersion model:\par
\pard\sb120\sa120\qc\i C(x,y,0) = Q / (pi * sigma_y * sigma_z * u) * exp(-y\super 2\nosupersub  / 2*sigma_y\super 2\nosupersub ) * exp(-H\super 2\nosupersub  / 2*sigma_z\super 2\nosupersub )\i0\par
\pard\sb60\sa60 Where:\par
\pard\li360\sb30\sa30\bullet  Q = emission rate (kg/s)\par
\bullet  sigma_y, sigma_z = dispersion coefficients (determined by stability class)\par
\bullet  u = wind speed (m/s)\par
\bullet  H = effective stack height (m)\par
\pard\sb60\sa60 Two modes are supported:\par
\pard\li360\sb30\sa30\bullet  \b SteadyState\b0  \u8212? Continuous emission, time-independent concentration\par
\bullet  \b Transient\b0  \u8212? Puff release with configurable duration, time-dependent spreading\par
\pard\keepn\sb360\sa120\b\fs32 11. CSharpNumerics API Reference\b0\fs24\par
\pard\sb60\sa60 The simulation pipeline uses the CSharpNumerics RiskScenario fluent API:\par
\pard\sb60\sa30\f1\fs20 var result = RiskScenario\line     .ForGaussianPlume(emissionRate)\line     .FromSource(position)\line     .WithWind(speed, direction)\line     .WithStability(StabilityClass.D)\line     .WithMaterial(Materials.Radioisotope("Cs137"))\line     .WithVariation(v => v\line         .WindSpeed(min, max)\line         .WindDirectionJitter(degrees)\line         .EmissionRate(min, max)\line         .SetStabilityWeights(d: 0.6, c: 0.2, e: 0.2))\line     .OverGrid(geoGrid)\line     .OverTime(startSec, endSec, stepSec)\line     .RunMonteCarlo(iterations, seed)\line     .AnalyzeWith(clusteringGrid, evaluator)\line     .Build(threshold: 1e-6);\f0\fs24\par
\pard\sb120\sa60\b Key Namespaces:\b0\par
\pard\li360\sb30\sa30\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Engines.GIS.Scenario\f0  \u8212? RiskScenario, RiskScenarioResult\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Engines.GIS.Simulation\f0  \u8212? PlumeSimulator, PlumeMode\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Engines.GIS.Analysis\f0  \u8212? ProbabilityMap, ScenarioClusterResult\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Engines.GIS.Grid\f0  \u8212? GeoGrid, GridSnapshot\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Engines.GIS.Export\f0  \u8212? GeoJsonExporter, CesiumExporter\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Physics.Enums\f0  \u8212? StabilityClass (A\endash F)\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Physics.Materials\f0  \u8212? Materials.Radioisotope()\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.ML\f0  \u8212? ClusteringGrid, KMeans, SilhouetteEvaluator\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Numerics.Objects\f0  \u8212? Vector, Matrix\par
\bullet  \f1 CSharpNumerics.Statistics.MonteCarlo\f0  \u8212? MonteCarloSimulator\par
\pard\sb120\sa60\b Querying Results:\b0\par
\pard\li360\sb30\sa30\bullet  \f1 result.ProbabilityAt(position, timeSeconds)\f0  \u8212? Query probability at a point\par
\bullet  \f1 result.ProbabilityMapAt(timeIndex)\f0  \u8212? Get probability grid for a time step\par
\bullet  \f1 result.ClusterAnalysis.DominantCluster\f0  \u8212? Get the dominant cluster\par
\bullet  \f1 result.ExportGeoJson(path)\f0  \u8212? Export to GeoJSON\par
